801
01:08:19.166 --> 01:08:21.002
So. either way is good.

802
01:08:21.069 --> 01:08:25.205
Okay. uh. hope you're having
a good one. All right. bye.

803
01:08:33.280 --> 01:08:36.050
A patient
with AB negative blood type

804
