923
01:20:25.192 --> 01:20:31.131
Okay. so in this video there
was an act of violence.

924
01:20:31.198 --> 01:20:35.269
Yes. and it made me want to
hurt someone too.

925
01:20:38.906 --> 01:20:40.974
I see.

926
01:20:41.041 --> 01:20:46.213
You know. sometimes
when I go for a run. um.

927
01:20:46.280 --> 01:20:50.518
to pump myself up. I daydream
about getting into a fight.

928
01:20:50.585 --> 01:20:54.188
defending my wife. punching
some jerk for accosting her.

929
01:20:54.254 --> 01:20:56.857
It's quite a common fantasy.
but it's not a healthy one.

930
01:20:56.924 --> 01:21:01.596
