991
01:27:35.056 --> 01:27:39.560
but this job taught me that
not everyone deserves...

992
01:27:39.627 --> 01:27:40.828
help.

993
01:27:40.895 --> 01:27:44.999
Some people deserve
the opposite.

994
01:27:45.066 --> 01:27:47.668
I realize that's not the best
thing to say in a job interview.

995
01:27:47.735 --> 01:27:49.503
but what I'm getting at is:

996
01:27:49.570 --> 01:27:53.373
I have learned how to hold
myself and others to task.

997
01:27:53.440 --> 01:27:55.342
That's a good skill. Very good.

998
01:27:55.375 --> 01:27:57.211
Another thing I learned:

999
01:27:57.344 --> 01:27:58.713
There are three types of people:

1000
01:27:58.780 --> 01:28:01.448
people who make the world
better.

1001
01:28:01.516 --> 01:28:03.350
people who make the world worse.

1002
01:28:03.416 --> 01:28:05.953
and people who watch.

1003
01:28:06.020 --> 01:28:08.956
Most people. they watch.

1004
01:28:10.224 --> 01:28:12.392
That's it. That's all they do.

1005
01:28:13.828 --> 01:28:16.363
I would rather be
one of the other two.

1006
01:28:17.598 --> 01:28:19.366
Let me make sure
I have this correct:

1007
01:28:20.067 --> 01:28:23.771
You'd rather make the world
worse than do nothing?

1008
01:28:23.838 --> 01:28:25.206
Yes.

1009
01:28:25.273 --> 01:28:27.374
Okay. now you lost me.

1010
01:28:27.407 --> 01:28:30.211
Well. bad things happen
no matter what.

1011
01:28:30.278 --> 01:28:33.214
And sometimes the only way to
stop a bad thing...

1012
01:28:33.281 --> 01:28:35.917
...is with another bad thing.

1013
01:28:35.983 --> 01:28:39.086
You know. I'm not sure I agree
with you there.

1014
01:28:39.153 --> 01:28:41.122
Well. I figured you wouldn't.

1015
01:28:41.189 --> 01:28:43.591
-Is that right?
-Yeah.

1016
01:28:45.492 --> 01:28:47.528
As interesting
as all this may be.

1017
01:28:47.595 --> 01:28:51.032
I don't quite understand how
it pertains to the question I
asked.

1018
01:28:51.098 --> 01:28:54.902
Or our meeting. Or
a career in your desired field.

1019
01:28:54.969 --> 01:28:56.971
Oh no. it's related.

1020
01:28:57.038 --> 01:29:00.808
Well. you might think so. but
I'm not seeing it.

1021
01:29:02.610 --> 01:29:04.745
Trust me. it's all related.

1022
01:29:23.631 --> 01:29:28.936
[sinister music rises]

1023
01:33:09.890 --> 01:33:12.126
[objects clattering]

1023
